<!doctype html>
<html>
{{> head }}
<body id="index">
  {{> header }}
  <div class="content">
    <section id="subtitle">
      <h1 class="xl">Offline magic code collaboration.</h1>
      <p>A free and open-source way to host, share, and build software together.</p>
    </section>
    <section id="get-the-app">
      <div id="email-signup">
        <p>Interested in using Radicle?</p>
        <form>
          <input type="text" placeholder="Enter your email"><button>Sign up</button>
        </form>
      </div>
      <img src="/img/org-project-page.png" alt="app image">
    </section>
    <section id="value-prop">
      <h1>Why Radicle?</h1>
      <p>It’s not easy to switch to something new, but here’s why you should.</p>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="value-prop-item">
          {{> svg-p2p }}
          <h2>Peer-to-peer</h2>
          <p>No servers. No platforms. No in-betweens. Share your code without relying on a third party.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-prop-item">
          {{> svg-local-first }}
          <h2>Local-first</h2>
          <p>All of your issues, revisions, and reviews exist on your computer. You own your data — nobody else.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-prop-item">
          {{> svg-easy-to-use }}
          <h2>Secure</h2>
          <p>No need to trust anyone to keep your work safe. Everything is signed and backed by public key cryptography.</p>
        </div>
      </div>{{! closes container }}
      <img id="main-illustration" src="/img/garden1.png" alt="A beautiful garden.">
    </section>{{! closes value prop section }}
    <section id="tech">
      <h1>No more walled gardens.</h1>
      <p>Radicle is an open-source stack for code collaboration. Anyone can build on it.</p>
      <button>How Radicle Works</button>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="tech-item">
          {{> svg-registry }}
          <h2>Registry</h2>
          <p>For hosting & collaboration, we built Radicle Link, a peer-to-peer replication protocol built on git.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tech-item">
          {{> svg-link }}
          <h2>Link</h2>
          <p>For decentralized identity & project organization, we built the Radicle Registry.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section id="dogfooding">
      {{> svg-dogfooding }}
      <h1>We’re dogfooding</h1>
      <p>To build a great product, we have to use it ourselves. We're building Radicle with our own tech. Help us out and try out our alpha <a href="https://github.com/radicle-dev/radicle-upstream" target="_blank">here</a>.</p>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="value-prop-item">
          {{> svg-beta1 }}
          <h5 class="all-caps">June 2020</h5>
          <h2>1st Beta Release</h2>
          <p>The core feature-set on top of a peer-to-peer stack. This is when we'll start using it ourselves.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-prop-item">
          {{> svg-beta2 }}
          <h5 class="all-caps">September 2020</h5>
          <h2>2nd Beta Release</h2>
          <p>Everything a code collaboration tool needs including notifications, search, and discovery.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-prop-item">
          {{> svg-beta3 }}
          <h5 class="all-caps">December 2020</h5>
          <h2>2nd Beta Release</h2>
          <p>The app will be hooked up with real money and the public registry and we’ll launch our native coin.</p>
        </div>
      </div>{{! closes container }}
    </section>{{! closes value prop section }}
  </div>{{! closes content }}
  {{> footer }}
</body>
</html>
